      <title>抑郁症试验成功，制药商 Intra Cellular 股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/drugmaker-intra-cellular-soars-as-depression-trial-succeeds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在其最畅销药物在重度抑郁症试验中取得成功后，细胞内疗法公司 (Intra-Cellular Therapies Inc.) 的股价创下两年多以来的最大涨幅，这可能会开辟一个利润丰厚的新市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/drugmaker-intra-cellular-soars-as-depression-trial-succeeds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 13:51:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
